# ============================================
# SOLANA DEX (Encrypted - DO NOT edit manually)
# ============================================
# Private key is now stored in .encrypted_keys file
# Bot will prompt for password on startup
# 
# Current wallet: 83zkAaLqhi29AURTbwFp2eAt8uRntp9pS7iQcgoWbNZJ
# 
# To update: python secure_key_loader.py encrypt --key SOLANA_PRIVATE_KEY --value "YOUR_PRIVATE_KEY"
